<h1><span property="schema:name">Frailty</span>
</h1>
</div>
<div id="block-medsites-content" class="widget block">
<article data-history-node-id="2991" role="article" about="/commodorecompendium/frailty" typeof="schema:WebPage">
<div>
<div property="schema:text" class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"><div style="border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:double windowtext 1.5pt; border-left:none; border-right:none; padding:1.0pt 0in 1.0pt 0in">
<p style="border:none; padding:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Functional Status and Frailty</span></span></b></span></span></span></p>
</div>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Background</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Frailty</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">: Syndrome of physiological decline in late life, characterized by marked vulnerability to adverse health outcomes</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Functional status: Ability to perform activities necessary in daily life (ADL)</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Pts should be encouraged to exercise as tolerated, with a low threshold to refer to PT/OT</span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Evaluation</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Order Vitamin D &amp; B-12 levels</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Vulnerable Elders Scale-13: Identifies community dwelling pts at risk for decline over 5 yrs</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Fried Frailty Tool: Identifies frailty in community dwelling elders (1 -2 = prefrail; &gt; 3 = frail)</span></span></span></span></span>
<ul style="list-style-type:circle">
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Fatigue:  are you Fatigued? </span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Resistance: are you unable to climb a flight of stairs? </span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Aerobic: are you unbale to walk a block ? </span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Illness: Do you have more than 5 illnesses ? </span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Loss: Have you lost more than 5% of weight in 6 months?</span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
